<p class="normalText"><h2>Intro & Consent</h2></p>
<p class="normalText"><h3><p> </p>
</h3></p>
<p class="normalText"><br/></p>
<p class="normalText"><p><br><br></p></p>
<p class="normalText" style="background-color: #FFE066;padding: 5px;border: 1px solid black;">ID: 5</p>
<p class="normalText"><h4>I agree to participate in this survey*</h4></p>
<p class="normalText"> [ ] I agree</p>
<p class="normalText"><p><br><br></p></p>
<p class="normalText"><hr></p>
<p class="normalText"><h2>Qualifying Questions</h2></p>
<p class="normalText"><h3></h3></p>
<p class="normalText"><br/></p>
<p class="normalText" style="background-color: #b7a5c9;padding: 5px;border: 1px solid black;"><strong>Page exit logic: </strong>Skip / Disqualify Logic<strong>IF: </strong> <span class="logic-id-seperator"></span>Question "Which region do you live in?" is one of the following answers ("A non metro area")<strong> THEN: </strong> Disqualify and display: "Sorry, you do not qualify to take this survey." </p>
<p class="normalText"><p><br><br></p></p>
<p class="normalText" style="background-color: #b7a5c9;padding: 5px;border: 1px solid black;"><strong>Page exit logic: </strong>Skip / Disqualify Logic<strong>IF: </strong> <span class="logic-id-seperator"></span>Question "Do you or does anyone in your household work in any of the following industries?" is one of the following answers ("Market research or opinion polling","Advertising or marketing","Food or grocery manufacturing","Retail (grocery or supermarket)")<strong> THEN: </strong> Disqualify and display: "Sorry, you do not qualify to take this survey." </p>
<p class="normalText"><p><br><br></p></p>
<p class="normalText" style="background-color: #b7a5c9;padding: 5px;border: 1px solid black;"><strong>Page exit logic: </strong>Skip / Disqualify Logic<strong>IF: </strong> <span class="logic-id-seperator"></span>Question "What is your age group?" is one of the following answers ("Under 30","50+")<strong> THEN: </strong> Disqualify and display: "Sorry, you do not qualify to take this survey." </p>
<p class="normalText"><p><br><br></p></p>
<p class="normalText" style="background-color: #b7a5c9;padding: 5px;border: 1px solid black;"><strong>Page exit logic: </strong>Disqualify — not target gender<strong>IF: </strong> <span class="logic-id-seperator"></span>Question "Which best describes you?" is not one of the following answers ("Female")<strong> THEN: </strong> Disqualify and display: "Sorry, you do not qualify to take this survey." </p>
<p class="normalText"><p><br><br></p></p>
<p class="normalText" style="background-color: #FFE066;padding: 5px;border: 1px solid black;">Shortname / Alias: Gender</p>
<p class="normalText" style="background-color: #FFE066;padding: 5px;border: 1px solid black;">ID: 14</p>
<p class="normalText"><h4>Which best describes you?*</h4></p>
<p class="normalText"> ( ) Female</p>
<p class="normalText"> ( ) Male</p>
<p class="normalText"> ( ) Non-binary or Gender diverse</p>
<p class="normalText"> ( ) Prefer not to say</p>
<p class="normalText"><p><br><br></p></p>
<p class="normalText" style="background-color: #FFE066;padding: 5px;border: 1px solid black;">Shortname / Alias: Age</p>
<p class="normalText" style="background-color: #FFE066;padding: 5px;border: 1px solid black;">ID: 16</p>
<p class="normalText"><h4>What is your age group?*</h4></p>
<p class="normalText"> ( ) Under 30</p>
<p class="normalText"> ( ) 30-34</p>
<p class="normalText"> ( ) 35-39</p>
<p class="normalText"> ( ) 40-44</p>
<p class="normalText"> ( ) 45-49</p>
<p class="normalText"> ( ) 50+</p>
<p class="normalText"><p><br><br></p></p>
<p class="normalText" style="background-color: #FFE066;padding: 5px;border: 1px solid black;">Shortname / Alias: Industry_Screen</p>
<p class="normalText" style="background-color: #FFE066;padding: 5px;border: 1px solid black;">ID: 18</p>
<p class="normalText"><h4>Do you or does anyone in your household work in any of the following industries?</h4></p>
