<p class="normalText"><h2>Screener</h2></p>
<p class="normalText"><h3></h3></p>
<p class="normalText"><br/></p>
<p class="normalText" style="background-color: #b7a5c9;padding: 5px;border: 1px solid black;"><strong>Page exit logic: </strong>Disqualify — no Core category selected<strong>IF: </strong> <span class="logic-id-seperator"></span>Question "Which of the following food and grocery categories have you personally bought or been responsible for buying in the last 12 months? Please select all that apply.<br />
 " is not one of the following answers ("Dry Seasonings & Spices","Pour Over Sauces","Pasta Sauces","Baking Mixes")<strong> THEN: </strong> Disqualify and display: "Sorry, you do not qualify to take this survey." </p>
